15.title: End Experiment
15.content: Thanks for participating in our study!

17.title: Instructions 1
17.content:
Instructions

In the following experiment, you will see three pictures on the screen on every trial. Your task is to identify which of these three images is different and indicate your answer by pressing one of the following keys: V (left), G (center) or B (right).

After you have indicated your choice, you will receive feedback and you will also get to know the IDs for each picture on screen.

Press "Space" to start the experiment
